{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "bms-shree-nandi-v1",
    "name": "Business Management System – Shree Nandi",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the Shree Nandi Business Management System backend.\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Set the `base_sng_url` variable to `http://127.0.0.1:8080`.\n2. Call **Login** or **Register** – the `token` variable is set automatically via the test script.\n3. All protected requests use `{{token}}` via the collection-level Authorization header.",
